                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/4499" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-0640</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9843 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">并购估值和商誉减值：坚瑞沃能的亏损黑洞</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">M &amp; A valuation and goodwill impairment of J&amp;R Optimum Energy’s losing black hole</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">方慧，陈子颖，陆叶，阎蓓蓓</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">上海大学MBA教育管理中心</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">刘焱</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">陕西坚瑞沃能股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">电子工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">并购估值；减值迹象；商誉减值；坚瑞沃能；沃特玛</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">M&amp;A valuation;Corporate Value Assessment; Goodwill Impairment; J&amp;R Optimum Energy;OptimumNano Energy Co.,Ltd.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2016年收购沃特玛，坚瑞沃能一度成为创业板明星公司，被冠以A股“锂电巨头”。然而，从风光无限的“锂电巨头”成为破产边缘的重组公司，坚瑞沃能仅仅用了不到2年的时间。究竟是谁推动坚瑞沃能走向了巨额亏损的深渊？并购沃特玛过程中的过高估值以及后续的巨额商誉减值计提无疑成为了大家讨论的焦点。本案例通过详细分析坚瑞沃能在并购沃特玛过程中的估值问题以及商誉减值的测试及计提，旨在引导学生在理解和掌握估值和商誉减值计提对企业财务影响的背景下，学会如何评价并购估值的合理性，如何判断商誉减值迹象以及减值计提的合理性，从而能对进一步加强企业合并过程中并购估值和商誉减值计提的监管提供借鉴。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">With the acquisition of OptimumNano Energy Co.,Ltd in 2016, J&amp;R Optimum Energy was once a gem star company, branded an A-share &quot;lithium giant.&quot; However, from the glorious &quot;lithium giant&quot; to the bankruptcy of the restructuring company, it only took less than two years for J&amp;R Optimum Energy. Who propels J&amp;R Optimum Energy to the abyss of huge losses?.The valuation premium in the process of M &amp; A and the subsequent large amount of impairment of goodwill have undoubtedly become the focus of discussion. In this case, through detailed analysis of the valuation issues ,and the accrual of goodwill impairment of J&amp;R Optimum Energy during the acquisition of OptimumNano Energy Co.,Ltd.The purpose is to guide students to understand and master the acquisition valuation and the impairment of goodwill to the company. In the context of financial impact, learn how to evaluate the rationality of M &amp; A valuation, how to judge the signs of goodwill impairment and the reasonableness of impairment provision, so as to further strengthen the governance of the value of M &amp; A and goodwill impairment as a reference.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2019</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务会计》、《财务报表分析》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">并购估值、商誉减值</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020-06</td>
                            </tr>
